||'''[[Psylocke#Joining the Exiles|Psylocke]]''' (Earth-616)
||Elisabeth "Betsy" Braddock
||''Exiles'' #90
||From [[Excalibur (comics)#New Excalibur (2005)|New Excalibur]]. Powers and abilities include: telekinesis, a mastery of [[ninjutsu]], and an immunity to telepathy, reality alterations, and spells.
