{{fnb|1}}The longest time a team has been together 

{{fnb|2}}Issues #23-25 and #38-40 focused on Weapon X with no appearances by the Exiles

{{fnb|3}}Issues #41 and #42 feature Nocturne telling Blink her story at the time of the beach break in issue #11, Blink and Nocturne are the only Exiles featured during this story and only appear in "present" in #42.

{{fnb|4}}Tanaraq control Sasquatch's body in issues 57-59. He is then purged from her body by Shaman and she loses her powers

{{fnb|5}}Thanks to a device made by the Squadron Supreme, Proteus believes himself to be Morph

{{fnb|6}}This line indicates the operator of the Panoptichron

{{fnb|7}}Nocturne rejoined the team in Die by the Sword #5 (swapping with Longshot) but left with Blink and T-Bird for a vacation on Heather's Earth in Exiles #100.

